
What is a Read me file?

The Readme file is often the first file which the users read. It is a text file that contains the information for the user about the software, project, code, game, or it might contain instructions, help, or details about the Patches or updates  patches or updates.

Why is it neccessary?

It is necessary because it immediately serves as a source of communication to all intending users long after the developer has moved on
